{"type":"message","id":"28c183ae","parentId":"0494fb4c","timestamp":"2026-04-21T15:43:18.682Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`prompt-optimizer` exists as a skill. Let me spawn it as a sub-agent to clarify the user's request. But wait - the user is asking a straightforward question about which project is most stable. The question is fairly clear already. Let me still follow the AGENTS.md workflow and use prompt-optimizer to formalize/clarify the request, then present it back to the user for confirmation.\n\nActually, thinking about this more carefully - the user's question is quite clear. They want to know which of 5 project ideas is the most \"stable\" (ổn định). I can understand this without needing a prompt-optimizer. But AGENTS.md says to always use prompt-optimizer for new requests.\n\n\nI'll go ahead and spawn the prompt-optimizer agent now to formalize this request.","thinkingSignature":"ab736ddc5e8264b6ec7657f09456eddb16b85867b79959a7a719a7d7cb8fffe6"},{"type":"text","text":"OK, `prompt-optimizer` có sẵn. Tôi spawn nó để cụ thể hóa yêu cầu của bạn:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8h3loj5gel7a_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator && openclaw agents spawn prompt-optimizer --help 2>&1 | head -5","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":196,"output":273,"cacheRead":13345,"cacheWrite":458,"totalTokens":14272,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776786193046,"responseId":"0636ce11ade9be71844b11ba57d5d6fe"}}
