{"type":"message","id":"d69e4457","parentId":"fa447d0d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:04:52.410Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to coordinate with other agents to build a quick demo of S1 (AI Safety Monitoring System). This is a multi-step task that requires multiple agents working together.\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md workflow rules, I need to use prompt-optimizer first to clarify the requirements before starting. But the user has already been quite specific - they want a quick demo of S1. The context is clear enough at this point.\n\nActually, let me reconsider. The AGENTS.md says:\n1. Làm rõ trước → Spawn prompt-optimizer\n2. Xác nhận → Gửi kết quả cho user\n\n\n3. Chờ OK → Chỉ bắt đầu làm khi user xác nhận\n\nThe user is saying \"bạn thực hiện kết hợp với các agent khác thực demo nhanh sản phẩm s1\" - they're asking me to execute S1 demo quickly using other agents. I think I should still clarify the scope before diving in, but the intent is pretty clear from their message.\n\nLet me think through what's needed for this demo: a Python backend handling real-time camera streams with YOLO detection for PPE gear, a React dashboard showing alerts and camera feeds, and a mobile notification system for real-time updates. I should lay out the architecture and get confirmation before spinning up multiple agents.","thinkingSignature":"f34799ceea6adb2fcb083bb40df5d611e85b6803bafc9381e52ee0279ef9a869"},{"type":"text","text":"Tôi cần làm rõ trước theo workflow — nhưng yêu cầu khá rõ ràng rồi, nên tôi sẽ trình **kiến trúc + kế hoạch** để bạn xác nhận trước khi spawn agents.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pfitw6ysjel6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ 2>/dev/null","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":432,"cacheRead":3682,"cacheWrite":18277,"totalTokens":22391,"cost":{"inpu