{"type":"message","id":"391affb4","parentId":"b17a5c5d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:07:02.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user confirmed:\n1. MongoDB - they will provide (so we won't use the existing one)\n2. Camera source - video file\n3. Output location - workspaces2/projects\n4. Git - no, temporary, don't push to GitLab\n\nNow I need to spawn agents. Let me plan the workflow:\n\n1. **senior-backend** → Build Python/Flask detection engine with YOLOv8 + video file input\n2. **senior-frontend** → Build React dashboard (can run in parallel after backend API is defined)\n3. **senior-devops** → Docker compose\n\n\n4. **senior-qa** → Smoke tests\n\nI could do the backend and frontend in parallel since the frontend just needs the API spec, but the devops depends on having the services ready first. Let me think about whether it's cleaner to run everything sequentially or let the frontend start while the backend is being built.\n\nActually, the most efficient approach is to spawn the backend agent first, wait for it to finish and publish the API spec, then launch the frontend agent with that spec in hand while the backend is still running. The QA and devops agents can come after.\n\nWait, I'm overcomplicating this. The orchestrator workflow says I should spawn agents for concurrent tasks without waiting for each one to complete. So I can launch backend, frontend, and devops all at the same time, then QA last once everything's ready.\n\nFor S1, that means spawning the backend and frontend agents in parallel to start working on the Python/Flask detection engine and React dashboard simultaneously.\n\nThe backend needs to handle video file processing with YOLOv8 for PPE detection across three classes, stream results via Flask-SocketIO to MongoDB, and expose a REST API. The frontend should display camera feeds in a grid, show a real-time alert list, and include basic statistics. I'll spawn both agents now and pass the key requirements to each.","thinkingSignature":"90efcb7aa41ae6493c9012b35cf5e5ee04c27b042645756cb7f94f5737d8263a"},{"type":"text","text":"OK, confirmed. Spawning agents ngay:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nb16ltvzegir_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/{backend,frontend,devops}","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":468,"cacheRead":21606,"cacheWrite":1892,"totalTokens":23966,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776787610725,"responseId":"0636d39be9cd6c549d20ca2d726e5918"}}
