{"type":"message","id":"894b6ffb","parentId":"8b65d4bb","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:07:08.618Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now spawn the agents. I'll spawn backend and frontend in parallel, then devops after.\n\nLet me spawn:\n1. senior-backend → /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/backend\n2. senior-frontend → /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/frontend\n\nI need to give each agent a detailed prompt with:\n- What to build\n- Tech stack\n- File locations\n- What's expected\n\nFor the backend, I need to include:\n- Python 3.11 + Flask\n- OpenCV + YOLOv8 (ultralytics)\n\n\n- Flask-SocketIO for real-time communication\n- MongoDB (user will provide the connection)\n- Video file processing to detect helmet, vest, and person\n- REST API endpoints and a Socket.IO event schema\n\nFor the frontend, I'll need:\n- React 18 + Vite + Ant Design\n- Real-time dashboard with camera feed grid, alert list, and stats\n- WebSocket connection via Socket.IO client\n- Mock video file path for demo purposes\n\nLet me figure out the right command syntax for spawning agents.","thinkingSignature":"44617ea75b51b1836a6d6c3354c738c92e5901fbe08d44233196f95edcbc5d21"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_endrm2y17j97_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator && openclaw agents spawn --help 2>&1 | head -30","yieldMs":8000,"timeout":12}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":50,"output":315,"cacheRead":22811,"cacheWrite":1123,"totalTokens":24299,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776787622747,"responseId":"0636d3a785bd6cd9d9213ff61da2cc5d"}}
