{"type":"message","id":"95232f1f","parentId":"f088a95c","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:09:14.620Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me just start implementing S1 directly. I'll create all the necessary code files for a complete demo.\n\n**Backend (Python/Flask):**\n- `app.py` - Flask app with REST API and WebSocket\n- `detector.py` - YOLOv8 detection engine\n- `video_processor.py` - Video file processing\n- `models.py` - MongoDB models\n- `requirements.txt`\n- `Dockerfile`\n\n**Frontend (React/Vite):**\n- `App.jsx` - Main dashboard\n- `components/CameraGrid.jsx` - Camera feeds\n- `components/AlertList.jsx` - Real-time alerts\n\n\n- `components/StatsBar.jsx` - Statistics\n- `App.css`\n- `package.json`\n\n**Devops:**\n- `docker-compose.yml`\n- `.env.example`\n\nLet me start creating all these files.","thinkingSignature":"0299f2e0a1b2a740bc4f01a6a5f7df5a8c0ad71201f4623c1a29cc016dfe34b1"},{"type":"text","text":"Bắt đầu implement S1 ngay:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3sukp5l4k4ed_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/backend/requirements.txt","content":"flask==3.0.3\nflask-socketio==5.3.6\nflask-cors==4.0.1\npython-socketio==5.11.2\nopencv-python==4.9.0.80\nultralytics==8.1.43\npython-engineio==4.9.1\npymongo==4.6.2\npython-dotenv==1.0.1\neventlet==0.35.2\nPillow==10.3.0\nnumpy==1.26.4\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":54,"output":366,"cacheRead":29968,"cacheWrite":675,"totalTokens":31063,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776787748003,"responseId":"0636d424fc621e9efd54d6e3636ff1d2"}}
