{"type":"message","id":"e83b9ed2","parentId":"e2065afc","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:53:16.305Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The backend is now processing the video and detecting people in real-time! It found 4 people with 3 compliant and 1 violation (the person without helmet). Let me report this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"365fc5294646b4822fd868c542fe611f5643422b047455953a1c0c7af4cd82ff"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ Video đang chạy!\n\n**Backend đang xử lý video tự động:**\n\n```\nTổng người: 4\nTuân thủ: 3  ✅\nVi phạm: 1   ❌ (thiếu mũ)\nTỷ lệ: 75%\nFrame: 120/150\n```\n\n### 🔗 Truy cập ngay\n\n- **Dashboard:** http://103.253.21.139:3003\n- **Backend:** http://103.253.21.139:5000\n\nVideo là **15 giây** — backend sẽ loop lại từ đầu sau khi hết. Dashboard sẽ hiển thị thống kê realtime.\n\nVào dashboard xem kết quả nhé! 🎥"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":669,"output":231,"cacheRead":102517,"cacheWrite":294,"totalTokens":103711,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776790389207,"responseId":"0636de76817938a5b3bd0485d7f4d9ce"}}
