{"type":"message","id":"8080802f","parentId":"fd7e19a7","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:55:21.687Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add the `/api/frame` endpoint in app.py. Let me add it after the `/api/summary` endpoint.","thinkingSignature":"682e30572186248ad09c01ad1349ba1ae717447d37ffb0de3fd68ed0991abc63"},{"type":"text","text":"Now add the `/api/frame` endpoint in app.py:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_33uso0te2pe9_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/backend/app.py","edits":[{"oldText":"@app.route(\"/api/summary\", methods=[\"GET\"])\ndef get_summary():","newText":"@app.route(\"/api/frame\", methods=[\"GET\"])\ndef get_annotated_frame():\n    \"\"\"Return latest annotated frame as JPEG image.\"\"\"\n    if not processor:\n        return jsonify({\"error\": \"Processor not initialized\"}), 503\n    try:\n        frame_bytes = processor.get_latest_annotated_frame_bytes()\n        if frame_bytes is None:\n            return jsonify({\"error\": \"No frame available\"}), 503\n        return Response(frame_bytes, mimetype='image/jpeg')\n    except Exception as e:\n        return jsonify({\"error\": str(e)}), 500\n\n\n@app.route(\"/api/summary\", methods=[\"GET\"])\ndef get_summary():"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":75,"output":293,"cacheRead":105115,"cacheWrite":468,"totalTokens":105951,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776790515300,"responseId":"0636def451922ac9db625cd7b8dff582"}}
{"type":"message","id":"922d60f3","parentId":"8080802f","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:55:21.729Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_33uso0te2pe9_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/backend/app.py."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 173     except Exception as e:\n 174         return jsonify({\"error\": str(e)}), 500\n 175 \n 176 \n+177 @app.route(\"/api/frame\", methods=[\"GET\"])\n+178 def get_annotated_frame():\n+179     \"\"\"Return latest annotated frame as JPEG image.\"\"\"\n+180     if not processor:\n+181         return jsonify({\"error\": \"Processor not initialized\"}), 503\n+182     try:\n+183         frame_bytes = processor.get_latest_annotated_frame_bytes()\n+184         if frame_bytes is None:\n+185             return jsonify({\"error\": \"No frame available\"}), 503\n+186         return Response(frame_bytes, mimetype='image/jpeg')\n+187     except Exception as e:\n+188         return jsonify({\"error\": str(e)}), 500\n+189 \n+190 \n 177 @app.route(\"/api/summary\", methods=[\"GET\"])\n 178 def get_summary():\n 179     \"\"\"Get latest detection summary from running processor.\"\"\"\n 180     if not processor:\n     ...","firstChangedLine":177},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776790521712}}
{"type":"message","id":"51040a5c","parentId":"922d60f3","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:55:28.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to update the frontend App.jsx to show the actual video feed. The current `LiveFeedCanvas` draws boxes on a blank canvas using polling. I need to change it to:\n\n1. Show the actual video file\n2. Overlay bounding boxes from the detection data\n\nThe best approach:\n1. Use an HTML `<video>` element or `<img>` element showing the annotated frame\n2. Poll `/api/frame` every 500ms for the latest annotated frame\n3. Or use `<img>` with src=\"/api/frame\" and add detection overlays on top\n\nActually, for a smooth experience:\n- Show the video element with the source video","thinkingSignature":"40999a58aa1eac19a4644fb4d283bf05834b27cebb61a6572c82a12ec95c7d22"},{"type":"text","text":"Now update frontend to show real video with real detection overlay:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lmtcx8fq4h2i_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/src/App.jsx","offset":65,"limit":70}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":74,"output":215,"cacheRead":105368,"cacheWrite":551,"totalTokens":106208,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776790521738,"responseId":"0636defbdfc983fd23580d5ea4e09f47"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a61493b3","parentId":"51040a5c","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:55:28.714Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lmtcx8fq4h2i_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// ── Live Feed Canvas ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction LiveFeedCanvas({ summary }) {\n  const canvasRef = useRef(null)\n  const [frameSrc, setFrameSrc] = useState(null)\n  const intervalRef = useRef(null)\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    // Poll annotated frame from backend every 2s\n    intervalRef.current = setInterval(async () => {\n      try {\n        const data = await fetchAPI('/api/summary')\n        if (data.detections?.length > 0) {\n          // For demo: show a placeholder visualization on canvas\n          const canvas = canvasRef.current\n          if (!canvas) return\n          const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d')\n          const w = canvas.width\n          const h = canvas.height\n\n          // Background\n          ctx.fillStyle = '#1a1a2e'\n          ctx.fillRect(0, 0, w, h)\n\n          // Grid\n          ctx.strokeStyle = '#16213e'\n          ctx.lineWidth = 1\n          for (let i = 0; i < w; i += 40) {\n            ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(i, 0); ctx.lineTo(i, h); ctx.stroke()\n          }\n          for (let i = 0; i < h; i += 40) {\n            ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(0, i); ctx.lineTo(w, i); ctx.stroke()\n          }\n\n          // Draw detection boxes (scaled to canvas)\n          const scaleX = w / 1280\n          const scaleY = h / 720\n          data.detections.forEach(d => {\n            const [x1, y1, x2, y2] = d.bbox.map((v, i) => i % 2 === 0 ? v * scaleX : v * scaleY)\n            const ppe = d.ppe_status\n            ctx.strokeStyle = ppe.compliant ? '#00c853' : '#ff1744'\n            ctx.lineWidth = 2\n            ctx.strokeRect(x1, y1, x2 - x1, y2 - y1)\n            ctx.fillStyle = ppe.compliant ? 'rgba(0,200,83,0.15)' : 'rgba(255,23,68,0.15)'\n            ctx.fillRect(x1, y1, x2 - x1, y2 - y1)\n            // Label\n            ctx.fillStyle = ppe.compliant ? '#00c853' : '#ff1744'\n            ctx.font = 'bold 11px monospace'\n            const label = ppe.compliant ? '✓ OK' : `✗ ${!ppe.has_helmet ? 'NO-HELMET' : ''} ${!ppe.has_vest ? 'NO-VEST' : ''}`\n            ctx.fillText(label.trim(), x1 + 2, y1 - 4)\n          })\n\n          // Stats overlay\n          const s = data.summary || {}\n          ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)'\n          ctx.fillRect(8, 8, 180, 70)\n          ctx.fillStyle = '#fff'\n          ctx.font = '12px monospace'\n          ctx.fillText(`Persons: ${s.total_persons || 0}`, 16, 28)\n          ctx.fillStyle = '#00c853'\n          ctx.fillText(`Compliant: ${s.compliant || 0}`, 16, 46)\n          ctx.fillStyle = '#ff1744'\n          ctx.fillText(`Violations: ${s.violations || 0}`, 16, 64)\n        } else {\n          // No detections — show empty state\n          const canvas = canvasRef.current\n          if (!canvas) return\n          const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d')\n          ctx.fillStyle = '#1a1a2e'\n          ctx.fillRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height)\n          ctx.fillStyle = '#555'\n\n[316 more lines in file. Use offset=135 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776790528698}}
{"type":"message","id":"cd97998d","parentId":"a61493b3","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:55:38.352Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the current LiveFeedCanvas uses a canvas to draw detections, but the canvas just has a dark background with simulated grid. It doesn't show the actual video frames. I need to replace this with a proper video player that shows the actual annotated frames from the backend.Let me replace the LiveFeedCanvas with a component that:1. Shows the actual video file via a `<img>` element that polls `/api/frame` for annotated frames\n2. Overlays detection boxes on top (or the backend already draws boxes in the annotated frame)Actually, since I'm already returning annotated frames from the backend (with boxes drawn on them), I just need to:1. Replace the canvas approach with an `<img>` that polls `/api/frame`\n\n\n2. But wait—polling the backend every 500ms for the full annotated frame is inefficient and will cause flickering. A better approach would be to display the raw video with an overlay canvas for the detection boxes, then sync the boxes with the video playback using Socket.IO. This way I'm only sending bounding box coordinates instead of re-encoding the entire frame with detections every 500ms.\n\nFor the demo though, the simplest solution is to have the backend serve annotated frames and the frontend just display them via an img tag that polls every 500ms—it's not perfect but it'll work for showing detection boxes overlaid on the video.","thinkingSignature":"8cb3ae64e3370f865781085fbef16020e42fa478e6f920639b12e0fd28b3e841"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m49trepihggs_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/src/App.jsx","offset":1,"limit":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":909,"output":345,"cacheRead":105621,"cacheWrite":555,"totalTokens":107430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776790528722,"responseId":"0636df02c4ee8525014b6afa7989aff8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4fe68753","parentId":"cd97998d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:55:38.390Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_m49trepihggs_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { useState, useEffect, useRef } from 'react'\nimport { io } from 'socket.io-client'\nimport {\n  Layout, Card, Row, Col, Statistic, Table, Tag, Badge,\n  Button, Space, Typography, Alert, Progress, List, Timeline, Tooltip\n} from 'antd'\nimport {\n  SafetyOutlined, AlertOutlined, UserOutlined,\n  CheckCircleOutlined, StopOutlined, PlayCircleOutlined,\n  VideoCameraOutlined, ReloadOutlined\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\n\nconst { Header, Content, Sider } = Layout\nconst { Title, Text } = Typography\n\n\n[435 more lines in file. Use offset=16 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776790538373}}
{"type":"message","id":"452171c3","parentId":"4fe68753","timestamp":"2026-04-21T16:56:24.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me replace the LiveFeedCanvas function with a new one that shows the actual annotated frames from the backend. I'll also need to update the App.jsx to pass the API_BASE properly. Let me do a targeted replacement of the LiveFeedCanvas function.\n\nActually, let me just replace the whole component file with a cleaner version.","thinkingSignature":"f8817080b3df11dc7ae0a6ec9b33efbbc2a76cf67a978f888a4c6adc5afecd92"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5oyvkt2wtidi_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/s1-ppe-safety/frontend/src/App.jsx","content":"import { useState, useEffect, useRef } from 'react'\nimport { io } from 'socket.io-client'\nimport {\n  Layout, Card, Row, Col, Statistic, Tag, Badge,\n  Button, Space, Typography, Alert, Progress, List, Tooltip\n} from 'antd'\nimport {\n  SafetyOutlined, AlertOutlined, UserOutlined,\n  CheckCircleOutlined, StopOutlined, PlayCircleOutlined,\n  VideoCameraOutlined, ReloadOutlined, VideoAddOutlined\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\n\nconst { Header, Content, Sider } = Layout\nconst { Title, Text } = Typography\n\n// ── API helpers ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nconst API_BASE = import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE || ''\n\nasync function fetchAPI(path) {\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}${path}`)\n  if (!res.ok) throw new Error(`${path} → ${res.status}`)\n  return res.json()\n}\n\n// ── Stats Card ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction StatsCard({ title, value, icon, color, sub }) {\n  return (\n    <Card size=\"small\" style={{ borderRadius: 12 }}>\n      <Statistic\n        title={<Text type=\"secondary\" style={{ fontSize: 13 }}>{title}</Text>}\n        value={value}\n        valueStyle={{ color, fontSize: 28, fontWeight: 700 }}\n        prefix={<span style={{ marginRight: 8 }}>{icon}</span>}\n      />\n      {sub && <div style={{ marginTop: 4, fontSize: 12, color: '#888' }}>{sub}</div>}\n    </Card>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Alert Item ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfunction AlertItem({ alert }) {\n  const d = alert.detection || {}\n  const isViolation = !d.compliant\n  return (\n    <List.Item style={{ padding: '8px 0' }}>\n      <Space align=\"start\" style={{ width: '100%' }}>\n        <Badge status={isViolation ? 'error' : 'success'} />\n        <div style={{ flex: 1 }}>\n          <Space>\n            {d.has_helmet === false && <Tag color=\"red\">NO HELMET</Tag>}\n            {d.has_vest === false && <Tag color=\"orange\">NO VEST</Tag>}\n            {d.compliant && <Tag color=\"green\">OK</Tag>}\n          </Space>\n          <div style={{ fontSize: 11, color: '#999', marginTop: 2 }}>\n            {alert.timestamp ? new Date(alert.timestamp).toLocaleTimeString() : '—'}\n            {' · conf: '}{d.confidence?.toFixed(2) || '—'}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </Space>\n    </List.Item>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Video Feed — Shows actual annotated frames from backend ──────────────────\nfunction VideoFeed() {\n  const [imgSrc, setImgSrc] = useState(null)\n  const [lastUpdate, setLastUpdate] = useState(null)\n  const [error, setError] = useState(null)\n  const [frameCount, setFrameCount] = useState(0)\n  const [summary, setSummary] = useState(null)\n  const intervalRef = useRef(null)\n  const imgRef = useRef(null)\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    // Poll annotated frame + summary from backend every 500ms\n    intervalRef.current = setInterval(async () => {\n      try {\n        // Fetch annotated frame\n        const frameRes = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/api/frame`, { cache: 'no-cache' })\n        if (frameRes.ok) {\n          const blob = await frameRes.blob()\n          const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob)\n          setImgSrc(url)\n          setLastUpdate(new Date().toLocaleTimeString())\n          setError(null)\n          setFrameCount(c => c + 1)\n        }\n      } catch (e) {\n        // Silently ignore polling errors\n      }\n\n      try {\n        // Fetch latest summary\n        const summaryRes = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/api/summary`)\n        if (summaryRes.ok) {\n          const data = await summaryRes.json()\n          if (data.summary && Object.keys(data.summary).length > 0) {\n            setSummary(data.summary)\n          }\n        }\n      } catch {}\n    }, 500)\n\n    return () => {\n      clearInterval(intervalRef.current)\n      if (intervalRef.current?.imgSrc) {\n        URL.revokeObjectURL(imgSrc)\n      }\n    }\n  }, [])\n\n  const complianceColor = summary\n    ? (summary.compliance_rate >= 80 ? '#52c41a'\n      : summary.compliance_rate >= 50 ? '#faad14' : '#ff4d4f')\n    : '#888'\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ position: 'relative', borderRadius: 12, overflow: 'hidden', background: '#000' }}>\n      {/* Actual video frame from backend */}\n      {imgSrc ? (\n        <img\n          ref={imgRef}\n          src={imgSrc}\n          alt=\"Live detection feed\"\n          style={{\n            width: '100%',\n            display: 'block',\n            minHeight: 360,\n            background: '#000',\n          }}\n        />\n      ) : (\n        <div style={{\n          width: '100%',\n          height: 360,\n          display: 'flex',\n          alignItems: 'center',\n          justifyContent: 'center',\n          background: '#1a1a2e',\n          color: '#555',\n          fontSize: 14,\n          flexDirection: 'column',\n          gap: 12,\n        }}>\n          <VideoCameraOutlined style={{ fontSize: 48 }} />\n          <span>Đang kết nối camera...</span>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* HUD overlay */}\n      <div style={{\n        position: 'absolute', top: 12, right: 12,\n        background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)',\n        borderRadius: 6, padding: '6px 12px',\n        fontSize: 11, color: '#0f0',\n        fontFamily: 'monospace',\n      }}>\n        ● LIVE · FPS: {(frameCount / 10).toFixed(1)}\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Summary HUD overlay (bottom left) */}\n      {summary && (\n        <div style={{\n          position: 'absolute', bottom: 12, left: 12,\n          background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.75)',\n          borderRadius: 8, padding: '10px 14px',\n          fontFamily: 'monospace', fontSize: 12,\n        }}>\n          <div style={{ color: '#fff', marginBottom: 4 }}>\n            👤 {summary.total_persons || 0} phát hiện\n          </div>\n          <div style={{ color: '#52c41a' }}>\n            ✅ Tuân thủ: {summary.compliant || 0}\n          </div>\n          <div style={{ color: '#ff4d4f' }}>\n            ❌ Vi phạm: {summary.violations || 0}\n          </div>\n          <div style={{ color: complianceColor, marginTop: 4 }}>\n            📊 Tỷ lệ: {summary.compliance_rate || 0}%\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* Update indicator */}\n      <div style={{\n        position: 'absolute', top: 12, left: 12,\n        background: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.6)',\n        borderRadius: 6, padding: '4px 10px',\n        fontSize: 10, color: '#aaa',\n        fontFamily: 'monospace',\n      }}>\n        Cập nhật: {lastUpdate || '...'}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\n// ── Main App ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nexport default function App() {\n  const [summary, setSummary] = useState({\n    total_persons: 0, compliant: 0, violations: 0,\n    no_helmet: 0, no_vest: 0, compliance_rate: 100,\n  })\n  const [alerts, setAlerts] = useState([])\n  const [status, setStatus] = useState('connecting')\n  const [alertStats, setAlertStats] = useState({})\n  const socketRef = useRef(null)\n\n  // ── Socket.IO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const socket = io(API_BASE || window.location.origin, {\n      transports: ['websocket', 'polling'],\n      reconnectionAttempts: 5,\n      reconnectionDelay: 2000,\n    })\n    socketRef.current = socket\n\n    socket.on('connect', () => {\n      console.log('[WS] Connected')\n      socket.emit('subscribe', { camera_id: 'demo-camera' })\n      setStatus('live')\n    })\n\n    socket.on('disconnect', () => {\n      console.log('[WS] Disconnected')\n      setStatus('stopped')\n    })\n\n    socket.on('detection_summary', (data) => {\n      if (data.summary) setSummary(data.summary)\n    })\n\n    socket.on('ppe_alert', (alert) => {\n      setAlerts(prev => [alert, ...prev].slice(0, 100))\n      // Play alert sound\n      try {\n        const audio = new Audio(\n          'data:audio/wav;base64,UklGRnoGAABXQVZFZm10IBAAAAABAAEAQB8AAEAfAAABAAgAZGF0YQoGAACBhYqFbF1fdJivrJBhNjVgodDbq2EcBj+a2'\n          + 'teleQABYq73zYpwAABervfNjngAAKDJ8s6LfAAAmMzqz4uBAACR0fLPi4IAAJvT7tCLhwAAndn20IuIAACk2/bRi4oAAK7e9tGLigAAs'\n          + '+OD20IuKAAC44vbQi4oAAMHj9tCLigAAxuT20IuKAADK5fbQi4oAAM/m9tCLigAA0Of20IuKAADU6fbQi4oAANbq9tCLigAA2Oz20I'\n          + 'uKAADd7vbQi4oAAODv9tCLigAA5fD20IuKAADp8fbQi4oAAO7y9tCLigAA8fP20IuKAADz9PbQi4oAAPb19tCLigAA+PX20IuKAA'\n          + 'D69vbQi4oAAPv39tCLigABAff39tCLigABBfj32IKKCQA='\n        )\n        audio.volume = 0.3\n        audio.play().catch(() => {})\n      } catch {}\n    })\n\n    return () => socket.disconnect()\n  }, [])\n\n  // ── Poll alerts ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const loadAlerts = async () => {\n      try {\n        const [alertsData, statsData] = await Promise.all([\n          fetchAPI('/api/alerts?limit=20'),\n          fetchAPI('/api/alerts/stats').catch(() => ({})),\n        ])\n        if (Array.isArray(alertsData)) setAlerts(alertsData)\n        if (statsData && !statsData.error) setAlertStats(statsData)\n      } catch {}\n    }\n    loadAlerts()\n    const interval = setInterval(loadAlerts, 10000)\n    return () => clearInterval(interval)\n  }, [])\n\n  const complianceColor = summary.compliance_rate >= 80 ? '#52c41a'\n    : summary.compliance_rate >= 50 ? '#faad14' : '#ff4d4f'\n\n  return (\n    <Layout style={{ minHeight: '100vh', background: '#0f0f1a' }}>\n      {/* ── Header ── */}\n      <Header style={{\n        background: '#1a1a2e',\n        borderBottom: '1px solid #2a2a4a',\n        display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'space-between',\n        padding: '0 24px',\n      }}>\n        <Space>\n          <SafetyOutlined style={{ fontSize: 24, color: '#faad14' }} />\n          <Title level={4} style={{ color: '#fff', margin: 0 }}>\n            PPE Safety Monitor\n          </Title>\n          <Badge\n            status={status === 'live' ? 'processing' : 'error'}\n            text={<Text style={{ color: status === 'live' ? '#52c41a' : '#ff4d4f', fontSize: 12 }}>\n              {status === 'live' ? 'LIVE' : status === 'connecting' ? 'CONNECTING' : 'STOPPED'}\n            </Text>}\n          />\n        </Space>\n        <Space>\n          <Tooltip title=\"Reload alerts\">\n            <Button\n              icon={<ReloadOutlined />}\n              onClick={() => fetchAPI('/api/alerts?limit=20').then(d => Array.isArray(d) && setAlerts(d))}\n            >\n              Reload\n            </Button>\n          </Tooltip>\n          <Tag icon={<VideoAddOutlined />} style={{ background: '#16213e', border: 'none', color: '#aaa' }}>\n            Demo Video\n          </Tag>\n        </Space>\n      </Header>\n\n      <Layout>\n        {/* ── Main Content ── */}\n        <Content style={{ padding: 20, background: '#0f0f1a' }}>\n          {/* Stats Row */}\n          <Row gutter={[16, 16]} style={{ marginBottom: 20 }}>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <StatsCard\n                title=\"Tổng người phát hiện\"\n                value={summary.total_persons}\n                icon={<UserOutlined />}\n                color=\"#1890ff\"\n              />\n            </Col>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <StatsCard\n                title=\"Tuân thủ (✓)\"\n                value={summary.compliant}\n                icon={<CheckCircleOutlined />}\n                color=\"#52c41a\"\n              />\n            </Col>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <StatsCard\n                title=\"Vi phạm (✗)\"\n                value={summary.violations}\n                icon={<StopOutlined />}\n                color=\"#ff4d4f\"\n                sub={summary.no_helmet > 0 ? `• Không mũ: ${summary.no_helmet}` : null}\n              />\n            </Col>\n            <Col xs={24} sm={12} md={6}>\n              <Card size=\"small\" style={{ borderRadius: 12 }}>\n                <Statistic\n                  title={<Text type=\"secondary\" style={{ fontSize: 13 }}>Tỷ lệ tuân thủ</Text>}\n                  value={summary.compliance_rate}\n                  suffix=\"%\"\n                  valueStyle={{ color: complianceColor, fontSize: 28, fontWeight: 700 }}\n                  prefix={<SafetyOutlined style={{ marginRight: 8 }} />}\n                />\n                <Progress\n                  percent={summary.compliance_rate}\n                  showInfo={false}\n                  strokeColor={complianceColor}\n                  style={{ marginTop: 8 }}\n                />\n              </Card>\n            </Col>\n          </Row>\n\n          {/* Video Feed + Alert Panel */}\n          <Row gutter={[16, 16]}>\n            <Col xs={24} lg={14}>\n              <Card\n                title={\n                  <Space>\n                    <VideoCameraOutlined />\n                    Camera Feed — Demo\n                  </Space>\n                }\n                style={{ background: '#1a1a2e', border: '1px solid #2a2a4a' }}\n                styles={{ header: { color: '#fff', borderBottom: '1px solid #2a2a4a' } }}\n              >\n                <VideoFeed />\n                <Alert\n                  message=\"Demo mode — video file. Kết nối IP camera thực tế qua /api/detect endpoint.\"\n                  type=\"info\"\n                  showIcon\n                  style={{ marginTop: 12 }}\n                />\n              </Card>\n            </Col>\n\n            <Col xs={24} lg={10}>\n              <Card\n                title={\n                  <Space>\n                    <AlertOutlined style={{ color: '#ff4d4f' }} />\n                    Cảnh báo thời gian thực\n                    <Badge count={alerts.length} style={{ backgroundColor: '#ff4d4f' }} />\n                  </Space>\n                }\n                style={{ background: '#1a1a2e', border: '1px solid #2a2a4a', height: '100%' }}\n                styles={{ header: { color: '#fff', borderBottom: '1px solid #2a2a4a' } }}\n                bodyStyle={{ maxHeight: 500, overflow: 'auto' }}\n              >\n                {alerts.length === 0 ? (\n                  <div style={{ textAlign: 'center', padding: 40, color: '#555' }}>\n                    <SafetyOutlined style={{ fontSize: 48, marginBottom: 12 }} />\n                    <div>Không có cảnh báo nào</div>\n                    <div style={{ fontSize: 12, marginTop: 4 }}>Hệ thống đang hoạt động bình thường</div>\n                  </div>\n                ) : (\n                  <List\n                    dataSource={alerts}\n                    renderItem={(item) => <AlertItem alert={item} />}\n                    locale={{ emptyText: 'Không có cảnh báo' }}\n                  />\n                )}\n              </Card>\n            </Col>\n          </Row>\n        </Content>\n\n        {/* ── Sidebar ── */}\n        <Sider\n          width={240}\n          style={{ background: '#1a1a2e', borderLeft: '1px solid #2a2a4a', padding: 16 }}\n        >\n          <Title level={5} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>Thống kê 24h</Title>\n          <Space direction=\"vertical\" style={{ width: '100%' }} size={12}>\n            <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n              <Statistic\n                title={<Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 12 }}>Tổng cảnh báo</Text>}\n                value={alertStats.total || alerts.length}\n                valueStyle={{ color: '#fff', fontSize: 24 }}\n              />\n            </Card>\n            <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n              <Statistic\n                title={<Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 12 }}>Không đội mũ</Text>}\n                value={alertStats.no_helmet || 0}\n                valueStyle={{ color: '#ff4d4f', fontSize: 24 }}\n              />\n            </Card>\n            <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n              <Statistic\n                title={<Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 12 }}>Không áo phản quang</Text>}\n                value={alertStats.no_vest || 0}\n                valueStyle={{ color: '#faad14', fontSize: 24 }}\n              />\n            </Card>\n\n            <div style={{ marginTop: 16 }}>\n              <Title level={5} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>Camera</Title>\n              <Card size=\"small\" style={{ background: '#16213e' }}>\n                <Space>\n                  <Badge status=\"success\" />\n                  <Text style={{ color: '#aaa', fontSize: 13 }}>demo-camera</Text>\n                </Space>\n                <div style={{ fontSize: 11, color: '#666', marginTop: 4 }}>1280×720 · Edge+Blob</div>\n              </Card>\n            </div>\n          </Space>\n        </Sider>\n      </Layout>\n    </Layout>\n  )\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":199,"output":4508,"cacheRead":105956,"cacheWrite":1442,"totalTokens":112105,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776790538399,"responseId":"0636df0b7f7a8465c16b5d53f5ca1ee1"}}
